{"tid":423213,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"<求幫助>想搵返一隻年代久遠既直昇機game","createTime":"2017-10-03T17:04:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-05T16:22:56.000Z","uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"92ee1c9abc0feaf4699a8f5c5aa05f0121ea7241","tid":423213,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T17:04:50.000Z","msg":"PC既....我諗應該係1998(前後2-3年)咁上下時間啦<br />\n<br />\n有十幾廿關<br />\n<br />\n隻game 用第3身控制直昇機,全game 得3款直昇機比你揀<br />\n<br />\n個分別就係裝甲薄同厚同埋可以用既武器<br />\n<br />\n第一款係輕型既直昇機<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.airforceworld.com/pla/gfx/gazelle/gazelle_8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.airforceworld.com%2Fpla%2Fgfx%2Fgazelle%2Fgazelle_8.jpg&h=b5a9693e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢款咁上下<br />\n<br />\n第2款係黑鷹<br />\n<br />\n第3款係阿帕奇<br />\n<br />\n打完一關有錢可以upgrade 埋直昇機同武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n直昇機可以降落補給回血<br />\n<br />\n玩到去後期有D 關會有個神秘波波係到入去會接左去其他神秘地方<br />\n<br />\n隻game係我童年回憶...細個因為唔識降落卡左係第2關好耐(第2關勝利條件要降落check point)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後誤打誤撞降落左又打到好後<br />\n<br />\n但之後去到有關要保護D飛彈發射車真係打唔贏就放棄左<br />\n<br />\n突然心血來潮想睇下之後D關係點<br />\n<br />\n但一直google 同係youtube search都冇<br />\n<br />\n想問下有冇巴打知道叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nthanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4d6b76e1b5fab8b419c8c49239ebd31de7cd26","tid":423213,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T17:06:13.000Z","msg":"有有十幾廿關係我打到去18/19咁上下所以我估有有十幾廿關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e0196eb3008af25d4bcb2662e5176b98613e0c","tid":423213,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T01:54:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bec4984710d8ca3a113149c92e26d422d7bb4f0","tid":423213,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T02:42:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3dce12981db2b813b27702b36ff07b843143ec5","tid":423213,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T03:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb3f070919d0ed6c69bd4dc5d8d248b592bd35b","tid":423213,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T06:41:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a6e51c27e4c059f8cd8f10c7a2b57e929328b7","tid":423213,"uid":82155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T06:49:47.000Z","msg":"ps1 嘅？<br />\n架飛機可以勾起d 野？？"},{"pid":"ae8d86529210c34e4d44fdd79a8adb48693c27bb","tid":423213,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T06:54:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ps1 嘅？<br />\n架飛機可以勾起d 野？？</blockquote><br />\n有人回我了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPC架...PS1應該冇<br />\n<br />\n唔可以勾起d 野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4bf41006ec6a8a0d54220422df1fbc59ccd993f","tid":423213,"uid":82155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T07:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />試下用 啲直升機嘅英文名 + pc +  年份去search ?"},{"pid":"cb426c37802f2623a93a42cfab7663524731d2d2","tid":423213,"uid":50428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T07:18:51.000Z","msg":"搭單幫手搵得唔得，有隻game 你係炮台黎 space 轉武器類型 係防止啲兵登錄。一個炮台要對好多飛機坦克咁 。禁實空白會bug左你支炮會冇左炮管 好似